                <img style="position: absolute; top: 80; right: 0; border: 0;" src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/38ef81f8aca64bb9a64448d0d70f1308ef5341ab/68747470733a2f2f73332e616d617a6f6e6177732e636f6d2f6769746875622f726962626f6e732f666f726b6d655f72696768745f6461726b626c75655f3132313632312e706e67" alt="Fork me on GitHub" data-canonical-src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/github/ribbons/forkme_right_darkblue_121621.png">
            </a>

            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <p>
                            <br/>

                        <div id="warning_testing" class="alert alert-danger" role="alert" style="display: none; text-align: center; font-weight: bold;">
						<h5><strong>This is NOT a production server. 
							This contains testing functionalities that may have bugs, and data may be outdated.
							<br />Camera-ready (production) page is located at <a href="http://aloja.bsc.es">http://aloja.bsc.es</a></strong></h5>
						</div>

                        <h4>Welcome to the <strong>ALOJA</strong> project,</h4>
                        
